{"tid":975871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★消息指中國全線新 iPhone 要降價了！比香港還要便宜","createTime":"2019-01-10T04:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T08:20:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d2da26cb989073b687c873cfd2f34e42dd1527","tid":975871,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"Jan 10, 2019<br />\n<br />\n自從蘋果宣佈調低第一季營收預期，更直指中國銷情放緩是原因之一，人們也關注新 iPhone 會否降價。來自《每日經濟新聞》的報導指 1 月 8 日晚上，華強北渠道收到美國方面的價格調整通知，iPhone XR、iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus、iPhone X、iPhone XS、iPhone XS 開始降價。三款全新 iPhone 也降兵，那就是蘋果回應中國市場的直接方法。<br />\n<br />\n今次降價以 iPhone XR 降價幅度最大，消息指「渠道價」下降了 450 元人民幣，現時售價為 5,250 人民幣（約 HK$6,040，比香港官方建議零售價 HK$6,499 還要低）。暫時未知蘋果會否直接將官方售價降低，現時中國區 Apple Online Store 所見，iPhone XR 64GB 版定價仍然是 6,599 人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n如果中國地區率先降價，那麼其他地區會否同樣開始考慮降價呢？也許這只是一個開始！隨著 2019 年來臨，人們會越來越期待 iPhone 2019 新版的出現，而今次相信蘋果非旦不能加價，甚至有機會降價！一直以來，蘋果只會在推出新一代 iPhone 時，才會將舊 iPhone 降價，但今次卻提前降價，反映今次蘋果的定價策略出現重大錯誤！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/01/10/china-iphone-price-drop/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2Fchina-iphone-price-drop%2F&d=XYjAR2kfDNRlBgPoxB6BaHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=15a3ce68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/01/10/china-iphone-price-drop/</a>"},{"pid":"35c9234afde499fab6d5c452047e265002797f67","tid":975871,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HcgwGs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HcgwGs.gif&h=e9f776cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWMkYmx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWMkYmx.gif&h=ddfd62a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUaaA8g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUaaA8g.gif&h=c1e76e9d&s